{"tid":238522,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［本土設計.香港時裝］ 真正屬於香港本土設計師的時裝展及市集","createTime":"2017-05-11T05:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T05:15:27.000Z","uid":115984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d691535b7194673eeb07f324406d666909b4fc5","tid":238522,"uid":115984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"提起香港時裝大家會諗到咩呢？<br />\n除左PMQ、K11、D2 Place之外， 其實重有d新一代既設計師需要支持！ <br />\n今次SPITGAN Magazine 將聯同 The Hive 一齊舉行 RUNWAY 3 ！ <br />\n<br />\nRUNWAY 3 將會系5月19-20號系西環堅尼地城 The Hive 舉行！<br />\n5月19號會有一個fashion show，全部都系本地designer 既作品！ <br />\n詳情同票務可以系我地既event page <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/166856213842042??ti=ia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F166856213842042%3F%3Fti%3Dia&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2e7e6e04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/166856213842042??ti=ia</a> 搵到。 <br />\n<br />\n跟住20號就系SPITGAM MARKET 既日子啦！ <br />\n我地搵左好多香港新一代既時裝設計師，帶佢地最自豪既作品來！ <br />\n而且當日重會有19號runway 既designer 做分享會<br />\n如果你鐘意fashion就記得來啦！<br />\n<br />\n地點/ 堅尼地城士美菲路12p祥興工業大廈6樓1室<br />\n時間/ 11-5pm<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Www.spitgan.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWww.spitgan.com&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0e75ef65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Www.spitgan.com</a> <br />\nInstagram/ @spitgan_magazine @spitgan_market <br />\nFacebook/ SPITGAN Magazine <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/11/131403_6bd3977d841174be3b571ffe7ca19903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F11%2F131403_6bd3977d841174be3b571ffe7ca19903.jpg&h=c91b2543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/11/131416_aae85696c11765f958c88af4c0555883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg